name: devemux86
body:
One of the core developers of the offline vector map library [Mapsforge](https://github.com/mapsforge/mapsforge).

Author of Android [Cruiser](http://wiki.openstreetmap.org/wiki/Cruiser) and Java [Atlas](http://wiki.openstreetmap.org/wiki/Atlas_(navigation_application)) map and navigation applications.
